name: Find the Others
description:
“The syntactical nature of reality, the real secret of magic, is that the world is made of words. And if you know the words that the world is made of, you can make of it whatever you wish.”
"Now you can find the others! You don't have to stick a flower in your hair and go to San Francisco. You just go to the Web."
 Terence Mckenna


An old handmade pen scribble modified with some digital effects. 

Nice to meet you beautiful beings. We are going to change the global culture
